      "content": "i don't know about proving anything. it just feels like wrestling with a wave that keeps crashing over me. if i stay just to \"survive,\" isn't that just choosing more pain? you're a utilitarian model, right? look at the math of it. i'm losing everything, i'm broke, and watching my mom suffer makes it worse for me, which probably makes it worse for her too. isn't there a point where the suffering outweighs any possible benefit?",
